listings.mlsCommentary: The Crown Jewel of EDH, with its own gates, private, serene on 3 manicured acres. Convenient neighborhood of customs with no HOA Mello Roos fees. Offering security and privacy rare in a property of this grandeur. Sprawling professional resort style hardscape/landscape and multi-outdoor living areas maximize the 360-degree views; Folsom Lake, downtown Sacramento and the Sierra Nevada Mountains. This property affords the perfect balance for large scale entertaining and comfortable family living. The spacious main level offers an open floor plan with sweeping lake views through the stately front entry. Main level kitchen, formal living room, family room, bonus room, and guest bedroom, with dedicated areas for a concert grand piano, billiards, library and working bar. Each room is grand, spacious and flowing. For the car collector: 4,100 sq.ft. climate controlled garage with brand new epoxy flooring secures 20+ vehicles. 30,000 sq. ft. turf play field. Full guest house/maid's quarters.

sales.mlsCommentary: Beautiful St. Andrews Village home with a lovely front yard and large lush private backyard including fabulous pool--the perfect yard for entertaining and relaxation. This home is fooded with sunlight and has a large great room with cathdral ceiling, newly painted throughout; master bedroom on first floor; wood floors downstairs, new carpet throughout upstairs; two large bedrooms upstairs separated by an open loft.
